{"tid":2346294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉港警法案  美眾議院推翻特朗普否決 《國防授權法案》命運交參議院決定","createTime":"2020-12-30T07:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T10:03:33.000Z","uid":57677,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f02fa1ae30dd77de1dae2666c3eb38ddc7ec02a6","tid":2346294,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:07:41.000Z","msg":"美國眾議院周一推翻總統<span class=\"violet\">特朗普對</span>《國防授權法案》(NDAA)的<span class=\"violet\">否決。</span>獲參眾兩院兩黨議員廣泛支持的《國防授權法案》涵蓋廣泛，<span class=\"violet\">包括禁止向香港警察出口管制國防物品。</span><br />\n眾議院以三分二絕對多數票推翻特朗普的否決後，參議院預計本周表決，如果也推翻特朗普否決，將是國會在特朗普任內首次以三分二絕對多數票推翻他的否決。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxgXYRr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpxgXYRr.jpg&h=3641430d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201229/RNWD6RAKVNBNPDEZHSSTTGVFNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201229%2FRNWD6RAKVNBNPDEZHSSTTGVFNY%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=c6e9b80a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201229%2FRNWD6RAKVNBNPDEZHSSTTGVFNY%2F&h=c3f56f2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201229/RNWD6RAKVNBNPDEZHSSTTGVFNY/</a>"},{"pid":"ee85649edf8bd9a8d12f33e6f2675226256c9392","tid":2346294,"uid":57677,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:08:59.000Z","msg":"侵行緊乜棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n侵投共<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0955bc87c4779692eb5be7274b8b84a38d054206","tid":2346294,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"sorry trump, your time is up<br />\n<br />\nPOMPEO 2024"},{"pid":"4a6e7341d4138c12dee0fc66c5ca630960800cf1","tid":2346294,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci